1776372930800966	edict-dev	itc:v3:AWLkkmTOfzk5kQAAAAAAQeqtbv7rtAAAAAEvyAE		item.create	bn-1dtk	{"description":"Currently dev_loop/mod.rs breaks unconditionally on <promise>COMPLETE</promise>, while END_OF_STORY re-verifies with has_work(). Agents sometimes emit COMPLETE when bones remain (e.g., narrow framing around a phase). Make COMPLETE symmetric with END_OF_STORY: re-verify and continue the loop if work actually remains.","kind":"task","title":"dev-loop: verify has_work() before exiting on COMPLETE signal"}	blake3:Sv576_8CL0oxqr3fpAXU5pKbeUe7NJyZoRTd7wz_sBE
